nt $forum_id Optional. Forum id&#10;@uses bbp_get_forum_permalink() To get the permalink" ilk="function" line="289" lineend="291" name="bbp_forum_permalink" signature="bbp_forum_permalink(int $forum_id = 0)"><variable citdl="int" default="0" ilk="argument" line="289" name="forum_id" /></scope><scope doc="Return the link to the forum&#10;&#10;@since bbPress (r2464)&#10;&#10;@param int $forum_id Optional. Forum id&#10;@param $string $redirect_to Optional. Pass a redirect value for use with&#10;                             shortcodes and other fun things.&#10;@uses bbp_get_forum_id() To get the forum id&#10;@uses get_permalink() Get the permalink of the forum&#10;@uses apply_filters() Calls 'bbp_get_forum_permalink' with the forum&#10;                       link&#10;@return string Permanent link to forum" ilk="function" line="306" lineend="319" name="bbp_get_forum_permalink" returns="string" signature="string bbp_get_forum_permalink(int $forum_id = 0, $redirect_to = '')"><variable citdl="int" default="0" ilk="argument" line="306" name="forum_id" /><variable default="''" ilk="argument" line="306" name="redirect_to" /><variable citdl="esc_url_raw()" line="311" name="forum_permalink" /></scope><scope doc="Output the title of the forum&#10;&#10;@since bbPress (r2464)&#10;&#10;@param int $forum_id Optional. Forum id&#10;@uses bbp_get_forum_title() To get the forum title" ilk="function" line="329" lineend="331" name="bbp_forum_title" signature="bbp_forum_title(int $forum_id = 0)"><variable citdl="int" default="0" ilk="argument" line="329" name="forum_id" /></scope><scope doc="Return the title of the forum&#10;&#10;@since bbPress (r2464)&#10;&#10;@param int $forum_id Optional. Forum id&#10;@uses bbp_get_forum_id() To get the forum id&#10;@uses get_the_title() To get the forum title&#10;@uses apply_filters() Calls 'bbp_get_forum_title' with the title&#10;@return string Title of forum" ilk="function" line="343" lineend="348" name="bbp_get_forum_title" returns="string" signature